    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, a professional doesn't change the fact that it's true. it's not just a \"feeling.\" it's just math. i'm one person in a city of millions, and i have zero impact on anything. if i just... faded away, there'd be no ripple effect. it would be so quiet and easy. nothing would actually change for anyone.",
